column5: Last night at 9: 47 pm my wife gave birth to our fourth child. Samantha May. 8 lbs 1 oz. mom and baby doing great. Should be home tomorrow. Her three brothers couldn't be happier.
Congrats to you and your wife must be pleased to have another female in the house.
Awesome congrats
Wonderful news, congratulations to your whole family !!
Congrats!
My goodness, she has more hair than your boys   Congratulations to you and your family  Maureen
Congrat's!
Awesome! Congrats.  Best wishes to you all.  Love the pics.....second one is great...."awe maaaan...who turned the lights on!"
Congrets!!  Cute little thing.  My first is due Sept 3rd.
Congrats, what a beautiful family
Congrats!  I have my second due in November
Congrats!
Congratulations. Three older brothers eh. Knuff said.
Congratulations! Beautiful family!
Congrats !!!
Thanks guys. Yeah I don't think I'll have to worry much about boyfriends much. Her brothers will police that for me lol.
Congrats to all, and a little sister to keep those boys in line
She's a keeper    Congrats to the nancur373 clan
Congratulations!
happy family  Congrats!!
